{
  "bio": [
    "Walter Kurtz co-founded RATIONAL GmbH alongside Siegfried Meister, establishing himself as a key figure and co-owner from the company's inception in 1973.",
    "He served as a partner of RATIONAL GmbH for 25 years (1973-1998), maintaining a significant role as an anchor shareholder and founding member throughout the company's evolution.",
    "Following the company's transition to an AG, he served as the Deputy Chairman of the Supervisory Board for nearly two decades, from 1998 until 2017.",
    "Since July 2015, Kurtz has contributed his expertise to the company's governance as a dedicated member of the Audit Committee of RATIONAL AG.",
    "In 2017, he assumed his current position as the Chairman of the Supervisory Board, where he continues to lead the strategic oversight of the organisation."
